This directory contains the epics product called iocLogAndFwdServer. It
has been mofified from the standard extension version to also log to cmlog
and/or Oracle.

It also contains a test program called iocLogServerLogMsg.

At the time this was put in CVS, the development environment was broken
on LCLS.  So, the way you make it is non-standard.

To make iocLogAndFwdServer, check the code out on lcls-builder and do gmake.

To buld the test program called iocLogServerLogMsg, execute the script
called build_iocLogServerLogMsg.prod.bash on lcls-builder.

